            "text": "# LangChain + Portkey\nfrom langchain_openai import ChatOpenAI\nfrom portkey_ai import createHeaders, PORTKEY_GATEWAY_URL\n\nllm = ChatOpenAI(\n    openai_api_base=PORTKEY_GATEWAY_URL,\n    openai_api_key=\"pk-live-...\",\n    default_headers=createHeaders(\n        api_key=\"pk-live-...\",\n        virtual_key=\"anthropic-vk-...\",\n    ),\n    model=\"claude-opus-4-8\",\n)\n\n# All LangChain traces are logged in Portkey with full prompt/response pairs\nresult = llm.invoke(\"Summarize the CAP theorem.\")\n"
